events.title: SZA - SOS Tour
events.description: Up-and-coming alt R&B chanteuse SZA is the latest contender for the burgeoning genre's crown, generating significant buzz with her silky voice, fresh beats, and mesmerizing performances. At her live shows SZA truly sizzles on ethereal, ominously beautiful tracks like "Babylon" and "Warm Winds", delivering her poetic lyrics with a confidence and ease that belie her recent arrival on the scene. She may be young, but there's nothing novice about her -- from her striking visual presentation to her deliciously raspy voice, SZA has all the markings of a star in the making.

events.title: Anime Wonder Festival
events.description: Anime Wonder Festival is Tucson Arizona's 2-day outdoor Anime festival launching on October 14-15th 2023! Join us in the celebration of the Anime & Japanese pop culture showcasing the arts with Main Stage Entertainment, Exhibitors, Artist Vendors, Cosplay, Music, Japanese & Asian Food, Games, and more! Join the great 2-day escape and jump into the awesome world of Anime.

events.title: Bollywood Mask Party
events.description:
Welcome to the most happening party of Arizona. A Bollywood party with masquerade theme. You never know who’s behind the mask….

Here is your chance to be creative with your masks and costumes. Guests will be allowed to carry their masks inside the venue. Masks would also be available for purchase at the venue. Masks are not mandatory.

events.title: Bridge Block Party! An Improv Comedy Show
events.description: Comedians perform dynamic and hilarious scenes - all made up in the moment! Shows are family friendly.
